--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- BUILDING
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  For the current platform:
  $ mvn clean assembly:assembly

  For a different platform (i.e. windows):
  $ mvn -P +windows,-linux clean assembly:assembly

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- RUNNING
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Unzip the target distribution.
  $ java -jar sshtunnel-VERSION.jar

